📈 Logistic Regression for Car Purchase Prediction

📌 Overview
This project demonstrates Logistic Regression to predict whether a customer will purchase a car based on factors such as age, salary, and credit score. The dataset car_purchase.csv contains financial and demographic data to help analyze customer purchasing behavior.

📂 Dataset
Ensure your dataset (car_purchase.csv) is structured as follows:

Age	Salary	Credit Score	Purchased
25	50000	650	0
30	60000	700	1
...	...	...	...
⚙️ Installation
Ensure you have Python installed along with the required dependencies:

 
pip install numpy pandas matplotlib scikit-learn
